nl.joshuaslik.UFMReckoning.backend.formation

Class Form4321

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.joshuaslik.UFMReckoning.backend.formation.Formation
      • nl.joshuaslik.UFMReckoning.backend.formation.Form4321

  • public class Form4321
extends Formation
    Formation met 4-4-2 where CB is Central Back
    RB is Right back player
    LB is Left back player
    CM is Central midfield player
    LM is left midfield player
    RM is right midfield player
    LW is left wing player
    RW is right wing player
    ORM is offensive right midfield
    OLM is offensive left midfield
    ST is striker
    Author:
    Bryan van Wijk
